OL,3,CLetters to heaven postbox unveiled in
OL,4,CChesterfield
OL,6,FA scheme to support grieving families
OL,7,Fpost letters to loved ones has been
OL,8,Flaunched in Derbyshire.
OL,10,FThree "letters to heaven" post boxes
OL,11,Fhave been installed at sites around to
OL,12,Fencourage people to write messages to
OL,13,Floved ones who have passed away.
OL,15,FTina Harris Horner contacted
OL,16,Fcouncillor Allan Ogle to ask for the
OL,17,Fletterboxes to be installed, after
OL,18,Flosing both her parents two weeks
OL,19,Fapart in 2021.
