OL,3,CLetters to heaven postbox unveiled in
OL,4,CChesterfield
OL,6,FHer seven-year-old nephew Luca posted
OL,7,Fwas the first to post a letter to his
OL,8,Fgrandparents.
OL,10,F"Grief is a challenging journey," she
OL,11,Fsaid. "One of which I've struggled
OL,12,Fwith myself since losing both my
OL,13,Fparents two weeks apart in 2021.
OL,15,F"Luca misses his nanna and grandad
OL,16,FHarris immensely, as do we all, so I
OL,17,Fknow he really appreciates this idea."
