OL,3,CLetters to heaven postbox unveiled in
OL,4,CChesterfield
OL,6,FThe white post boxes, where messages
OL,7,Fcan be dropped off, have been
OL,8,Finstalled at Boythorpe Cemetery,
OL,9,FStaveley Cemetery and Chesterfield and
OL,10,FDistrict Crematorium.
OL,12,FThe boxes are free for anyone to post
OL,13,Fa letter to their loved ones, or, if
OL,14,Fit is a special occasion, they can
OL,15,Fpost birthday cards, anniversary
OL,16,Fcards, Mother's Day and Father's Day
OL,17,Fcards, Christmas cards and holiday
OL,18,Fpostcards.
