OL,4,CChesterfield
OL,6,FThe council has asked people not to
OL,7,Fpost anything other than paper or
OL,8,Fcardboard in these boxes, as items
OL,9,Fleft in the boxes cannot be returned.
OL,11,FSimilar schemes have been set up
OL,12,Felsewhere in the UK, including a
OL,13,Fpostbox that was donated by Royal Mail
OL,14,Fand installed at Gedling Crematorium
OL,15,Fin Nottinghamshire.
OL,17,Fafter telling her mum she wanted to
OL,18,Fwrite to her grandparents who had
OL,19,Fpassed away.
